Localization.Name: Pingala Seeds
Localization.Description: Every aspect of the pingala follows the golden ratio resulting a visually arresting plant. This include its seeds which are highly sought after by plant collectors. Especially since attempts to cultivate the pingala in greenhouse environments has proven extremely difficult.
